entry.value: update cs_livy.cs_livy_statements set response='stg file deleted' where sessionid = '$[session_id}' and statementid = '${statement_id}' and description = '${description}.gz'

select sessionid,statementid, substring(description, '(.+[^.gz])') as description from cs_livy.cs_livy_statements where status like 'Session%not found.' and description like '%.gz' and response is null limit 1
update cs_audit.cs_audit_master set status='"ok"' where sessionid = '$[session_id}' and statement = '${statement_id}' and pk_merge_filename = '${description}.gz'

update cs_audit.cs_audit_master t1 set status = t2.resp from (select a.pk_merge_filename,a.sessionid,a.statement,b.resp from (select * from cs_audit.cs_audit_master where status = 'LOCK') a, (select split_part(split_part(response,',',1),':',2) as resp,sessionid,statementid from cs_livy.cs_livy_statements where response is not null and length(response) > 0) b where a.sessionid=b.sessionid and a.statement=b.statementid) as t2 where t1.sessionid=t2.sessionid and t1.statement=t2.statement and t1.pk_merge_filename=t2.pk_merge_filename
SELECT sessionid,statementid FROM cs_livy.cs_livy_statements where status = 'I' or status = 'running' or status = 'waiting' limit 100

UPDATE cs_livy.cs_livy_statements SET status= '${session_status}', response= '${output:length():gt(60):ifElse(${output:substring(0,60)}, ${output})}', updatetimestamp = current_timestamp where sessionid = '${session_id}' and statementid = '${statement_id}'

update cs_audit.cs_audit_win_master t1 set status = t2.resp from (select a.pk_merge_filename,a.sessionid,a.statement,b.resp from (select * from cs_audit.cs_audit_win_master where status = 'LOCK') a, (select split_part(split_part(response,',',1),':',2) as resp,sessionid,statementid from cs_livy.cs_livy_statements where response is not null and length(response) > 0) b where a.sessionid=b.sessionid and a.statement=b.statementid) as t2 where t1.sessionid=t2.sessionid and t1.statement=t2.statement and t1.pk_merge_filename=t2.pk_merge_filename

labels.label: Delete sessions more then the pool

entry.value: SELECT * FROM livy.livy_pool where enable='true' and pool_size >= allocated limit 1

update cs_livy.cs_livy_sessions set status='DELSESS' where sessionid in ( select sessionid from cs_livy.cs_livy_sessions where flowname = 'crowstrike' and sessionid not in (select sessionid from cs_livy.cs_livy_sessions where flowname = 'crowstrike' and status like 'Session % not found.') and status='idle' limit (select count(sess.count-pool.pool_size) as cnt from (select * from cs_livy.cs_livy_pool pool) pool, (select flowname,count(*) count from cs_livy.cs_livy_sessions where flowname = 'crowstrike' and sessionid not in (select sessionid from cs_livy.cs_livy_sessions where flowname = 'crowstrike' and status like 'Session % not found.' or status='DELSESS') group by flowname) sess where pool.flowname=sess.flowname and pool.pool_size <= sess.count))
